        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "The Payback",
        "Location": "LOCATION_COLORADO",
        "PublicId": "109586565573",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/Colorado_2/_scene_bull.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 1a8a827f-932e-49c0-a1b3-e3201795ae19).Image",
        "Description": "I knew it, the Romanian job was a setup. The five targets from the romanian job? All Czech diplomats in witness protection from having hits put out on them, and we shot them all dead while they were at a garden show. Whats worse is they stiffed the bill and now a platoon of the Czech military is hiding here in colorado, waiting for the signal to assault the headquarters of M13Delta. Kill the platoon&apos;s tactical and militant heads to disorganize them and force a retreat.",
